**Two-part fix:**

**Part 1: Add optimistic update to `createListAction` (ShoppingListContext.jsx lines 191-195)**
After `dbCreateList` returns the new ID, immediately add a temporary list object to the `lists` state so the UI updates instantly:
```js
const createListAction = async (name, emoji = null) => {
  if (!userId) return;
  const newId = await dbCreateList(userId, name, userEmail, emoji);
  // Optimistic update — add to state immediately
  setLists(prev => [...prev, { id: newId, name, emoji, owner_id: userId, created_at: new Date().toISOString() }]);
  setActiveListId(newId);
};
```
